seg000:B3F6 aWellIDSayThisS db 'Well, I\d say this sword is all right for a beginner./You get wha'
seg000:B437                 db 't you pay for./It\s your standard, maintenance-free sword. If mon'
seg000:B478                 db 'ey\s a problem, this one\s for you.'
seg000:B49B                 db  11h
seg000:B49C                 db  0Ch
seg000:B49D                 db 0FFh
seg000:B49E                 db 0FFh
seg000:B49F aThisOneIsJustA db 'This one is just a bit better than the Training Sword. Once you g'
seg000:B4E0                 db 'et the hang of it, it\s an easy one to wield. The price is a bit '
seg000:B521                 db 'higher, but you can\t lose on this one./Why not take it with you?'
seg000:B562                 db  11h
seg000:B563                 db  0Ch
seg000:B564                 db 0FFh
seg000:B565                 db 0FFh
seg000:B566 aYouLikeThisOne db 'You like this one?/A wise choice./This is a high grade product. I'
seg000:B5A7                 db 't\s one of my biggest sellers.'
seg000:B5C5                 db  11h
seg000:B5C6                 db  0Ch
seg000:B5C7                 db 0FFh
seg000:B5C8                 db 0FFh
seg000:B5C9 aOhIDBeMoreThan db 'Oh, I\d be more than happy to tell you about this one./This is a '
seg000:B60A                 db 'real man\s sword. It\ll topple monsters in the wink of an eye.'
seg000:B648                 db  11h
seg000:B649                 db  0Ch
seg000:B64A                 db 0FFh
seg000:B64B                 db 0FFh
seg000:B64C aYouVeGotALotOf db 'You\ve got a lot of grit I\d say. This one really packs a punch. '
seg000:B68D                 db 'A top-of-the-line sword for a top-of-the-line-swordsman. Will you'
seg000:B6CE                 db ' take it?'
seg000:B6D7                 db  11h
seg000:B6D8                 db  0Ch
seg000:B6D9                 db 0FFh
seg000:B6DA                 db 0FFh
seg000:B6DB aIsnTThatTheSwo db 'Isn\t that the sword you brought in with you?'
seg000:B708                 db  11h
seg000:B709                 db  0Ch
seg000:B70A                 db 0FFh
seg000:B70B                 db 0FFh
seg000:B70C aThisShieldIsSm db 'This shield is small and has limited defense capability. It\s not'
seg000:B74D                 db ' very durable -- unless it\s used with great skill, it won\t last'
seg000:B78E                 db ' long. It\s better than nothing, I guess.'
seg000:B7B7                 db  11h
seg000:B7B8                 db  0Ch
seg000:B7B9                 db 0FFh
seg000:B7BA                 db 0FFh
seg000:B7BB aWellItSSlightl db 'Well, it\s slightly better than the Clay Shield. Long ago, a well'
seg000:B7FC                 db '-known hero used it for a short time. You could do a lot worse.'
seg000:B83B                 db  11h
seg000:B83C                 db  0Ch
seg000:B83D                 db 0FFh
seg000:B83E                 db 0FFh
seg000:B83F aThisOneIsMoreO db 'This one is more of a general-use shield. It\s not the best one I'
seg000:B880                 db ' carry. I can\t really recommend it, I think it will soon be obso'
seg000:B8C1                 db 'lete.'
seg000:B8C6                 db  11h
seg000:B8C7                 db  0Ch
seg000:B8C8                 db 0FFh
seg000:B8C9                 db 0FFh
seg000:B8CA aThisShieldIsIn db 'This shield is in a class by itself. It is strong and light and e'
seg000:B90B                 db 'asy to use. This is a superior shield, the least a brave man shou'
seg000:B94C                 db 'ld have.'
seg000:B954                 db  11h
seg000:B955                 db  0Ch
seg000:B956                 db 0FFh
seg000:B957                 db 0FFh
seg000:B958 aHoYouVeGotQuit db 'Ho! You\ve got quite an eye for these things, I see. This shield '
seg000:B999                 db 'is not made of common iron. It is made of a magic metal called Ma'
seg000:B9DA                 db 'gane. Against ordinary weapons, it\s unbreakable.'
seg000:BA0B                 db  11h
seg000:BA0C                 db  0Ch
seg000:BA0D                 db 0FFh
seg000:BA0E                 db 0FFh
seg000:BA0F aThisShieldMake db 'This shield makes the mightiest swords seem like paper. It\s ligh'
seg000:BA50                 db 't as a feather and hard as a diamond. Used well, this one will la'
seg000:BA91                 db 'st you a lifetime.'
